                            <comment id="12719468" author="robertburrelldonkin" created="Mon, 15 Jun 2009 10:02:26 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;This patch insists that the implementation returns not null. When the format is unknown an IllegalArgumentException will be thrown. If the caller can recover from a badly formatted cluster this exception can be caught. Otherwise, it provides reasonable diagnostic information.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12720112" author="gsingers" created="Tue, 16 Jun 2009 14:12:50 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed revision 785197.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12720669" author="robertburrelldonkin" created="Wed, 17 Jun 2009 14:40:35 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Index: core/src/main/java/org/apache/mahout/clustering/kmeans/Cluster.java&lt;br/&gt;
===================================================================&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;#8212; core/src/main/java/org/apache/mahout/clustering/kmeans/Cluster.java	(revision 784487)&lt;br/&gt;
+++ core/src/main/java/org/apache/mahout/clustering/kmeans/Cluster.java	(working copy)&lt;br/&gt;
@@ -84,7 +84,7 @@&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;@return a new Canopy&lt;br/&gt;
    */&lt;br/&gt;
   public static Cluster decodeCluster(String formattedString) {&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;int beginIndex = formattedString.indexOf(&apos;[&apos;);&lt;br/&gt;
+    int beginIndex = formattedString.indexOf(&apos;{&apos;);&lt;br/&gt;
     String id = formattedString.substring(0, beginIndex);&lt;br/&gt;
     String center = formattedString.substring(beginIndex);&lt;br/&gt;
     char firstChar = id.charAt(0);&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/12410711/MAHOUT-65c.patch&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/12410711/MAHOUT-65c.patch&lt;/a&gt; reverted a bounds check&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12720670" author="robertburrelldonkin" created="Wed, 17 Jun 2009 14:41:27 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;This patch combines the &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/12410711/MAHOUT-65c.patch&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/12410711/MAHOUT-65c.patch&lt;/a&gt; change with the additional error checks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12754972" author="isabel" created="Mon, 14 Sep 2009 14:24:05 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Adjusted patch to current trunk version.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
